{"tid":2432294,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"容我再講一次：除非通過陳雲，否則香港無得救。","createTime":"2021-03-04T08:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T08:46:13.000Z","uid":381643,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8aff919e6754261923421185d6e074e9cf3689dc","tid":2432294,"uid":381643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:26:02.000Z","msg":"陳雲：今日，香港在自由經濟的全球俱樂部被正式革除會籍！除了通過陳雲，否則香港無得救。但由於香港人污衊和踐踏陳雲，故此香港注定無得救。<br />\n香港被美國制裁，今日更被美國傳統基金會將香港的自由指數與中國城市等同。香港在自由經濟的俱樂部被革除會籍。香港居榜首二十五年後跌排名，今年正式被除名，猶如股票被除牌，無得上市。<br />\n<br />\n那些高舉法治、靠官司謀生的泛民，被共產黨用法庭程序集體折磨，擺出一幅哭哭啼啼相。<br />\n這就是香港人污衊陳雲的報應的小小開始。<br />\n<br />\n容我再講一次：除非通過陳雲，否則香港無得救。"},{"pid":"a8a6c8ad0d3fac8af833d22281b84d5ced96d25c","tid":2432294,"uid":103207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0U1BTxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0U1BTxB.png&h=06c4243a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5077f8a30456d3a3788f459769dc879d450b43e5","tid":2432294,"uid":84572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:29:13.000Z","msg":"Noted"},{"pid":"772b55eb9b5b393825a6a1208a85716df0647870","tid":2432294,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5531caac1eb7d22080efd7216771f7e610aec0","tid":2432294,"uid":321374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqS9t9s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqS9t9s.jpg&h=1ebd4f78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b985446a1bf63de5452bcdc704d151e0246f6cf","tid":2432294,"uid":38218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pBUTbp0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBUTbp